R(n,k)-(k+1)=\sum_{j=0}^k\sum_{m=1}^\infty\frac{\alpha^m}{m!}2^{-mj}=\sum_{m=1}^\infty\frac{\alpha^m}{m!}\frac{2^m-2^{-km}}{2^m-1}.
